These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, milk, cola, 7up
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: epic, spy, adventure, family, superhero, disaster, musical
 1. the person drinking water is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking 7up##2
 2. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 3. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 4. the person drinking milk is between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
 5. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 6. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 7. the person watching epic movies is between the person watching family movies and the person watching adventure movies##2
 8. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 9. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
11. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | water | 7up | fanta    | hot-chocolate | milk   | cola    |
| Movie-Genre         | disaster  | spy   | family | epic | adventure   | musical | superhero |

