.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
City: marseilles, rome, new-york, venice, edinburgh, berlin, san-francisco
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: september, april, july, november, january, december, august
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is between the person traveling to berlin and the person who's birthday is in december##2
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person traveling to rome is in the middle##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
9. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| City          | edinburgh | new-york | berlin | rome | san-francisco | marseilles      | venice  |
| Birthday   | december | november  | august     | july     | january  | september | april |

