.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: martial-arts, crime, zombie, musical, animation, time-travel, satire
There 7 different types of food: grapes, raspberry, grapefruit, pomegranate, lettuce, kiwi, broccoli
 1. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
 3. the person eating lettuce is the person watching satire movies##1
 4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the person watching musical movies is the person eating pomegranate##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
 8. the person eating grapes is between the person eating broccoli and the person watching musical movies##2
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
10. the person watching crime movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | animation | martial-arts | crime   | musical | zombie | time-travel |
| Food           | lettuce | kiwi     | raspberry     | grapefruit | pomegranate   | grapes   | broccoli    |

