.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: reading, collecting, camping, writing, filmmaking, dancing, card-games
There are 7 different favourite colors: lavender, fuchsia, light-blue, apricot, ebony, orange, azure
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 3. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 5. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 6. the person who likes apricot is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who likes orange##2
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is in the middle##1
 8. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person who likes fuchsia##1
10. the person who likes lavender is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Hobby      | camping    | filmmaking  | writing  | reading  | card-games      | dancing       | collecting |
| Color   | ebony | apricot | orange | azure | lavender | light-blue | fuchsia  |

