4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the tower house##1
5. the cottage house is in the middle##1
6. the townhouse house is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
7. the palace house is on the left of the tower house##1
8. the ranch-style house is the person who likes pink##1
9. the person who likes ivory is the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Color   | pink      | ivory | emerald | lilac | purple      | yellow      | aquamarine |
| House     | ranch-style | townhouse | modern       | cottage | palace | tower | futuristic |

