 7. the person who growsorchid is the project-manager##1
 8. the architect is the person who growsdahlia##1
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person who growsdahlia and the analyst##2
10. the doctor is on the left of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
