 8. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 9. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes green##1
10. the person who likes lavender is between the person who likes orange and the person who likes green##2
11. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
